 First, we calculate the total cost for 12 hours without adding any additional fees. The cost is 1000 pesos. Since Cameron adds 70 pesos for every additional hour, we calculate the total additional cost for 12 hours as follows \text{Total additional cost} = 12 \times 70 \text{ pesos} 
